'''Arlequin'''是一種[[自由軟體|自由]]的[[種群遺傳學|種群遺傳學]]綜合[[數據分析|數據分析]]軟件<ref name="Antao2015">{{cite book|author=Tiago Antao|title=Bioinformatics with Python Cookbook|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=E90DCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA152|date=25 June 2015|publisher=Packt Publishing|isbn=978-1-78355-865-0|page=152|access-date=2019-01-10|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215132646/https://books.google.com/books?id=E90DCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA152|dead-url=no}}</ref>，提供[[GUI|GUI]]介面，以讓一般用戶也可以作生物群体间的多種測試及計算，例如：{{link-en|遗传分化系数|Fixation index}}（Fixation index，亦作F-statistics<ref name="Liu 2015" />，F<sub>st</sub>）、[[遺傳距離|遺傳距離]]、[[哈代-温伯格定律|哈代-温伯格平衡]]、[[連鎖不平衡|連鎖不平衡]]和[[成對差|成對差]]測試等<ref name="AroraBerka2006">{{cite book|author1=Dilip K Arora|author2=Randy Berka|author3=Gautam B. Singh|title=Bioinformatics|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QmrPjRYrqgUC&pg=PA86|date=15 August 2006|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-08-046370-4|page=86|access-date=2019-01-10|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215132646/https://books.google.com/books?id=QmrPjRYrqgUC&pg=PA86|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Arlequin由[[日内瓦大学|日内瓦大学]]遗传学与生物统计学实验室开发<ref name="Barnes2007">{{cite book|author=Michael R. Barnes|title=Bioinformatics for Geneticists: A Bioinformatics Primer for the Analysis of Genetic Data|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CN9sYPJdXs4C&pg=PA172|date=16 April 2007|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-0-470-02619-9|page=172|access-date=2019-01-10|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215132646/https://books.google.com/books?id=CN9sYPJdXs4C&pg=PA172|dead-url=no}}</ref>。現時本軟體的最新版本為3.5.2.2，於2015年8月22日以zip壓縮及安裝檔的形式發放<ref name="Arlequin35" />，只有Windows版本。[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]及[[Linux|Linux]]只提供命令式（3.5.2），而且只限於64-bit環境，分為「arlecore」<ref name="arlecore" />、「arlsumstat」<ref name="arlsumstat" />及說明文件三部份。

